<number box="[957,985,941,963]" pageId="14" pageNumber="519" value="86.0">86</number>
”; another with three labels, 
<typeStatus box="[1286,1330,942,963]" pageId="14" pageNumber="519">type</typeStatus>
label, “S. Katharin Funke 
<number box="[362,390,972,994]" pageId="14" pageNumber="519" value="86.0">86</number>
”, and “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Hb. Det. Rebel" authorityName="Hb. Det. Rebel" box="[463,846,972,994]" class="Insecta" family="Lepidoptera" genus="Myrmecopsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="519" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="polistes">Myrmecopsis polistes Hb. Det. Rebel</taxonomicName>
”, the last label with indecipherable words written in pencil and an “X”, also in pencil, indicating the incorrectness of the identification; last 
<typeStatus box="[1070,1206,1002,1024]" pageId="14" pageNumber="519">paralectotype</typeStatus>
with three labels, all handwritten “Blumenau 
<collectingCountry box="[448,543,1033,1055]" name="Brazil" pageId="14" pageNumber="519">Brasilien</collectingCountry>
